title: The Official Website of Dr Joe Dispenza
cleaned_text:
“When we stop doubting, we start believing in our new life. We behave as if it's possible – and we ultimately become it.” Our community members are the boldest, bravest, most open-hearted people we know. Here are just a few of their legendary Stories of Transformation.

Believing; behaving; becoming; breaking through. Whether you join us in person, online, or in your own sacred space at home … you, too, are part of the story.

opengraph.title: The Official Website of Dr Joe Dispenza
opengraph.description: Dr Joe holds a Bachelor of Science degree and is a Doctor of Chiropractic. His post graduate training includes the fields of neuroscience and neuroplasticity, quantitative electroencephalogram (QEEG) measurements, epigenetics, mind-body medicine, and brain/heart coherence.
